summary: Today I was baby-sit my cousin (4 years old) and he was pretty quiet on the carpet play with his trains so I have decide to...
body:
Today I was baby-sit my cousin (4 years old) and he was pretty quiet on the carpet play with his trains so I have decide to finish a fanfic that have started this morning.

During a really additive chapter I zone out and when I’ve finished and returned to the normale world I’ve notice one thing:

there was silence.

Anyone who know children know that silence is a really really bad thing. So I get up from the couch and call my cousin’s name: Alex.

Or better: I get up and think to call my cousin’s name. Because for truth I’ve call another name:

Loki.

Yeah, at 10 a.m. in the morning I’ve scream Loki’s name for call my little cousin.

Never in my life I’ve feel so embarrassed. Of course from today I’ll never, ever, read fanfiction during babysit again.

.

.

.

(For who is worried: Alex was only in his room to search his toys, so no disaster)

summary: The Savage Avengers Brings Conan, the Punisher, Venom, Elektra, Brother Voodoo, and Wolverine Together
title: The Savage Avengers Brings Conan, the Punisher, Venom, Elektra, Brother Voodoo, and Wolverine Together
body:
The Savage Avengers Brings Conan, the Punisher, Venom, Elektra, Brother Voodoo, and Wolverine Together #savageavengers #marvel #comics

After the Avengers meet Conan in the upcoming Avengers: No Road Home #6, it was expected we’d see more Conan in the Marvel Universe and today we’ve got exactly that.

Conan joins the Punisher, Venom, Elektra, Brother Voodoo, and Wolverine in Savage Avengers written by Gerry Duggan with art by Mike Deodato Jr. and a cover by David Finch.

Conan has returned to the Marvel Universe and his new…
